description: This is a special doujinshi written by hentai specialist, Mr. Kimirito. Some of you may have known him at the Hentai Fest panel, "The Hentai Trends in Japan." He has written and independently published EroManga no Genba (The Pornographic Comics Scene), which contains interviews with various people involved in the industry. The series, which started in 2009 and concluded in 2014, is an invaluable resource for researchers.

description:
Kerorins works arent just about being cute. Theyre erotic. Some characters are shy and embarrassed, and try to keep their voices down in public but cant help moving their hips. Others get more aggressive, and like it loud and raunchy. Whether its a manager and her subordinate in a shop or a lecherous tenant trying to get after his landlady, these stories about beautiful women flutter the heart.

Theyre naughty but sweet, and you cant help but love these girls and thats what Stop Quibbling About Love is all about.
